title: 32-Year-Old Unsatisfied Wife
description:
From Tadanohito:

More stuff similar to 33-Year-Old Lusty Housewife. A couple of two-shots, then six one-shots. Older woman seduces younger man often. Again, cheating stories aren't dark at all. All stories a little humorous. All situations are rather unique and done in Kuroki's cleanly drawn style. Light censorship.
